title: Cleveland planning commission approves early designs for lakefront bridge and convention hotel tunnel
text:
Cleveland planning commission approves early designs for lakefront bridge and convention hotel tunnel 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
The Cleveland City Planning Commission approved early conceptual designs for a lakefront pedestrian bridge now estimated to cost $33 million...
